<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-01-0221 </DOCNO><TEXT>The author deals with the relationship between administrative law andcriminal law in the field of environmental protection. He investigates,inter alia, problems of criminal responsibility for water pollution accordingto sec. 324 Criminal Code and for the unauthorized operation of installationsaccording to sec. 327 Paragraph 2 Criminal Code.</TEXT></DOC>